Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe Ebonyi State police command have arrested a fake police officer, Enyi Friday, who parades himself as an officer and deceives people in the state.
The native of Umunwagu Idembia community in Ezza South LGA of Ebonyi  was arrested for impersonation by Anyigor Lazarus, who is a Commander of Ebubeagu Security outfit in Ezza South LGA of Ebonyi State.
Enyi, who is not a police officer was caught wearing the uniform of a Police Corporal hence his arrest.
CP Aliyu Garba   in a statement signed and made available to journalists in Abakaliki on the weekend, through the police public relations officer, PPRO, SP Chris Anyanwu said the suspect has been handed over to the State Investigation and Intelligence Department for further investigation.
